Azure Data Factory Pipeline
Pipeline Flow
1.	Schedule trigger every 1 hour
2.	Execute Python ingestion script
3.	Copy data into Azure SQL
4.	Log ingestion status
5.	Send alert on failure
ADF Activities
Activity	          Purpose
Web Activity	      Trigger AQI API
Copy Activity	      Move API data to SQL
Stored Procedure	   Validate sensor data
Failure Alert	       Notify on pipeline failure
